Open your mouth.

91
00:08:26,208 --> 00:08:27,792
Is that chicken?

92
00:08:28,583 --> 00:08:29,625
Spit it out.

93
00:08:29,792 --> 00:08:30,792
Spit it out, Preeti.

94
00:08:30,833 --> 00:08:34,292
