139
00:12:27,000 --> 00:12:31,000
<i>Delhi Institute of Medical Science versus
Khalsa Institute of Medical Science.</i>

140
00:12:31,083 --> 00:12:32,875
<i>Amit Sharma,
captain of the Khalsa institute.</i>

141
00:12:32,958 --> 00:12:35,958
<i>Kabir Rajdheer Singh,
captain of the DIMS institute.</i>

142
00:13:09,958 --> 00:13:11,083
